    {
      "name": "Pasarela de Pagos",
      "description": "Flujo de pago completo.\n\nOPCIÓN A — Solo backend (rápido):\n  1. orden-pago: genera formularioDatos con campos AES encriptados\n  2. callback-pago-aprobado o callback-pago-rechazado: simulás la notificación del mock\n  3. Consultar-Estado: verificás el nuevo estado\n\nOPCIÓN B — Integración real con el mock Docker:\n  1. orden-pago: copiás el formularioDatos de la respuesta\n  2. Abrís el browser, pegás el snippet JS de la consola con los valores\n  3. El browser hace POST a localhost:3000, el mock muestra el formulario de tarjeta\n  4. Ingresás 4242 4242 4242 4242 (aprobada) o 4000 0000 0000 0002 (rechazada)\n  5. El mock llama automáticamente al callback del backend\n  6. Consultar-Estado: verificás el nuevo estado",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "orden-pago",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "// Guardar IDs principales",
                  "pm.environment.set('id_orden_pago', body.idOrdenPago);",
                  "pm.environment.set('url_pago',      body.urlPago);",
                  "",
                  "// Guardar campos del formulario para inspeccion o submit manual al mock",
                  "if (body.formularioDatos) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('form_comercio',    body.formularioDatos.Comercio);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('form_txn_id',      body.formularioDatos.TransaccionComercioId);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('form_monto',       body.formularioDatos.Monto);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('form_callback_ok', body.formularioDatos.CallbackSuccess);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('form_callback_ko', body.formularioDatos.CallbackCancel);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('form_url_exito',   body.formularioDatos.UrlSuccess);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('form_url_error',   body.formularioDatos.UrlError);",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 200',                     () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene urlPago',                  () => pm.expect(body.urlPago).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene formularioDatos',          () => pm.expect(body.formularioDatos).to.be.an('object'));",
                  "pm.test('formularioDatos tiene Comercio', () => pm.expect(body.formularioDatos.Comercio).to.exist);",
                  "pm.test('Monto encriptado',               () => pm.expect(body.formularioDatos.Monto).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('CallbackSuccess encriptado',     () => pm.expect(body.formularioDatos.CallbackSuccess).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "",
                  "console.log('=== ORDEN DE PAGO ===');",
                  "console.log('ID Orden:',   body.idOrdenPago);",
                  "console.log('URL Mock:',   body.urlPago);",
                  "console.log('nroTramite:', body.formularioDatos?.TransaccionComercioId);",
                  "console.log('Comercio:',   body.formularioDatos?.Comercio);",
                  "console.log('Campos del formulario:', Object.keys(body.formularioDatos || {}).join(', '));",
                  "",
                  "console.log('');",
                  "console.log('=== OPCION A: Simular callback desde Postman ===');",
                  "console.log('Ejecutá callback-pago-aprobado o callback-pago-rechazado.');",
                  "",
                  "console.log('');",
                  "console.log('=== OPCION B: Flujo real con el mock en localhost:3000 ===');",
                  "console.log('Pegá en la consola del browser (F12) el siguiente snippet,');",
                  "console.log('reemplazando los valores encriptados con los de formularioDatos:');",
                  "console.log('');",
                  "const fd = body.formularioDatos || {};",
                  "const snippet = `const form = document.createElement('form');",
                  "form.method = 'POST';",
                  "form.action = '${body.urlPago}';",
                  "const campos = ${JSON.stringify(fd, null, 2)};",
                  "for (const [k, v] of Object.entries(campos)) {",
                  "  const i = document.createElement('input');",
                  "  i.name = k; i.value = v;",
                  "  form.appendChild(i);",
                  "}",
                  "document.body.appendChild(form);",
                  "form.submit();`;",
                  "console.log(snippet);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token_ciudadano}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/solicitudes/{{id_solicitud}}/pago/crear",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "solicitudes",
                "{{id_solicitud}}",
                "pago",
                "crear"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "callback-pago-aprobado",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// En modo SIM el backend bypasea la validación HMAC (ver PagoService.validarFirmaHmac).",
                  "// Igual firmamos para simular el comportamiento real.",
                  "",
                  "var hmacSecret = pm.environment.get('hmac_secret') || 'clave-secreta-campus-2026';",
                  "var nroTramite = pm.environment.get('nro_tramite');",
                  "",
                  "var body = JSON.stringify({",
                  "    transaccionId: 123456,",
                  "    comercioId: nroTramite,",
                  "    monto: '1500.00',",
                  "    estado: 'approved',",
                  "    fecha: new Date().toISOString()",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "var hash = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(body, hmacSecret);",
                  "var firma = CryptoJS.enc.Hex.stringify(hash);",
                  "",
                  "pm.environment.set('callback_body', body);",
                  "pm.environment.set('hmac_firma', firma);",
                  "",
                  "console.log('Callback body:', body);",
                  "console.log('HMAC firma:', firma);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 — pago procesado', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    console.log('Pago APROBADO procesado correctamente.');",
                  "    console.log('La solicitud debería estar en estado PAGADO.');",
                  "    console.log('>>> Ejecutá Consultar-Estado para verificar.');",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 401) {",
                  "    console.log('ERROR: Firma HMAC rechazada. Verificar hmac_secret.');",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 404) {",
                  "    console.log('ERROR: Solicitud no encontrada. Verificar nro_tramite.');",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 400) {",
                  "    console.log('ERROR 400:', pm.response.text());",
                  "    console.log('Puede que la solicitud ya no esté en estado PENDIENTE.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-PlusPagos-Signature",
                "value": "{{hmac_firma}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{{callback_body}}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/webhooks/pluspagos/callback",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "webhooks",
                "pluspagos",
                "callback"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "callback-pago-rechazado",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var hmacSecret = pm.environment.get('hmac_secret') || 'clave-secreta-campus-2026';",
